{"tid":555443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部指日本借花蓮賑災公然製造一中一台違背原則","createTime":"2018-02-09T12:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T04:14:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":134,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea6d4796a3d216be4ff9b3f14787da88f09a7b0","tid":555443,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"外交部指日本借花蓮賑災公然製造一中一台違背原則<br />\n<br />\n2018-02-09 HKT 17:29<br />\n <br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽說，台灣花蓮發生强烈地震後，日本借賑災之名，在國際上公然製造「一中一台」，有關做法違背一個中國原則，違背日方在台灣問題上所作的承諾，中方對此極為不滿，已向日方提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽又說，中方敦促日方切實恪守中日四個政治文件確定的原則，立即糾正錯誤做法，不要給中日關係製造新的干擾。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1380093-20180209.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1380093-20180209.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6d6a2378\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1380093-20180209.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b95be8f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1380093-20180209.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a5cde9280b0315525d9c8e3cb2394ced61a29c7f","tid":555443,"uid":83251,"like":95,"dislike":0,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n日本幫台灣手<br />\n關你小支那撚事咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005f340441cf2fd170d10d55106ad22fa9a001c9","tid":555443,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a5cde9280b0315525d9c8e3cb2394ced61a29c7f","tid":555443,"uid":83251,"like":95,"dislike":0,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n日本幫台灣手<br />\n關你小支那撚事咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"e?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7961291330106f359ce7e21fc90ff2162fd61aac","tid":555443,"uid":35790,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180208/640_d59e04cd5fe04e3f65262b66c66fe75e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180208%2F640_d59e04cd5fe04e3f65262b66c66fe75e.jpg&h=cf810288&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f748674f5310fc3322f69801bb5d9084d8349043","tid":555443,"uid":71257,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:32:29.000Z","msg":"人地日本救援隊入到台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中共唔比入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf39809d9915b6f727fae67c709f4c179880641","tid":555443,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好咁cls啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a409f7e6121cd9f5b3db173907807d5ca347b46","tid":555443,"uid":35790,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"新加坡軍機飛抵花蓮 運送物資賑災[影]<br />\n<br />\n發稿：2018/02/09 15:18\t<br />\n更新：2018/02/09 17:58<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者王承中花蓮縣9日電）新加坡軍機載滿帳篷、醫療用品、口糧等物資，今天下午3時許飛抵花蓮機場，國軍與星方人員聯手卸下物資，副參謀總長執行官陳寶餘向星方表達感謝。軍機預計於下午5時餘離開。<br />\n<br />\n滿載救援物資的新加坡C-130軍機今天下午3時許在花蓮機場降落，待軍機在停機坪停妥後，國軍弟兄隨即與星方人員聯手將星方提供的賑災物資自飛機上卸下。<br />\n<br />\n空軍表示，此次星方派來的軍機只有一架，載滿3人、5人帳篷、醫療用品、戰備口糧及毛毯等賑災急需的物資。<br />\n<br />\n擔任國軍救災總督導的陳寶餘上將也到現場向星方人員握手致意，表達感謝，並由空軍第五戰術混合聯隊作戰科長胡中華上校向星方人員致贈紀念品。<br />\n<br />\n目前賑災物資已全部從機上卸下，星國軍機正在進行加油作業，預計在下午5時20分起飛離開花蓮。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/webphotos/800/20180209/52816905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2Fwebphotos%2F800%2F20180209%2F52816905.jpg&h=cbaf3aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/webphotos/800/20180209/12700784.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2Fwebphotos%2F800%2F20180209%2F12700784.jpg&h=7c089e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201802095004.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201802095004.aspx&d=DcIovIHe8v2fPO%2BdLmikT5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9415a3e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201802095004.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"cfcab7f44e08ddac32a575b0bd2ba51228e65a67","tid":555443,"uid":154264,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af3b9ffcfbb10110c920a4d8d0b7373704157e4d","tid":555443,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":120,"score":-120,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:42:49.000Z","msg":"平時各地天災又唔見日本咁熱衷震災，唯獨今次台灣地震就高調震災，講左d乜自己深透下"},{"pid":"85903fed24271acc03b17a4f204d75411fe44d85","tid":555443,"uid":154264,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed06df20a268a64dd08aad611cf24fb802662654","tid":555443,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"af3b9ffcfbb10110c920a4d8d0b7373704157e4d","tid":555443,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":120,"score":-120,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:42:49.000Z","msg":"平時各地天災又唔見日本咁熱衷震災，唯獨今次台灣地震就高調震災，講左d乜自己深透下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"medi